s_findings": "我已成功收集和加载与 UUID `36937f85-134` 相关的 Trace 数据。以下是初步发现的异常信息摘要:\n\n### 异常调用链数据\n#### 格式解释\n- **parent_pod**: 调用方 (上游组件)\n- **child_pod**: 被调用方 (下游组件)\n- **normal_avg_duration**: 正常时段的平均耗时 (ms)\n- **anomaly_avg_duration**: 异常时段的平均耗时 (ms)\n- **anomaly_count**: 异常数量\n\n#### 主要调用链异常\n1. `frontend-0 -> shippingservice-2`: 请求耗时显著增加\n   - **操作**: `hipstershop.ShippingService/GetQuote`\n   - **正常时长**: 220.46 ms\n   - **异常时长**: 627.0 ms (≈2.84 倍增长)\n   - **异常数量**: 2\n\n2. `recommendationservice-0 -> recommendationservice-0` (循环请求):\n   - **操作**: `/hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/ListProducts`\n   - **正常时长**: 2975.89 ms\n   - **异常时长**: 3644.7 ms (≈1.22 倍增长)\n   - **异常数量**: 2\n\n3. `checkoutservice-2 -> cartservice-0`:\n   - **操作**: `POST /hipstershop.CartService/EmptyCart`\n   - **正常时长**: 2409.51 ms\n   - **异常时长**: 8623.0 ms (**显著增长: 3.58 倍**)\n   - **异常数量**: 1\n\n4. `checkoutservice-2 -> productcatalogservice-2`\n   - **操作**: `hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/GetProduct`\n   - **正常时长**: 10547.94 ms\n   - **异常时长**: 19683.5 ms (**显著增长: 1.87 倍**）\n   - **异常数量**: 1\n\n5. `checkoutservice-2 -> shippingservice-2`:\n   - **操作**: `hipstershop.ShippingService/ShipOrder`\n   - **正常时长**: 228.29 ms\n   - **异常时长**: 944.0 ms (增长至4倍)\n   - **异常数量**: 1\n\n6. `frontend-0 -> frontend-0`\n   - **操作**: `hipstershop.RecommendationService/ListRecommendations`\n   - **异常耗时**: 9071.4 ms (**但较正常时长 124078 ms 减少**)\n   - **异常数量**: 1\n\n7. `checkoutservice-2 -> checkoutservice-2`\n   - 子模块内部耦合导致高延迟:\n     - **操作1**: `hipstershop.CartService/EmptyCart`, **异常增长：4.7 倍**\n     - **操作2**: `hipstershop.ShippingService/GetQuote`, **增长超5倍**\n\n---\n\n⚠ **交叉对比**和推断根因的详细分析将在下个阶段进行，目前仅为初步扫描数据。", "log_analysis_findings": "日志收集成功，以下是关键日志信息提取和初步分析。\n\n### 检测到的错误日志\n通过分析日志，与 UUID `36937f85-134` 相关的报错信息集中发生在 `adservice`，服务运行在 `aiops-k8s-07` 节点。以下是提取的原始日志内容：\n1. **Exception in thread \"Attach Listener\"**\n   - 内容：`java.lang.reflect.InvocationTargetException`\n   - 出现次数：2\n   \n2. **重复加载 Byteman agent 的异常**\n   - 内容：`Caused by: java.lang.Exception: Main : attempting to load Byteman agent more than once`\n   - 出现次数：2\n   \n3. **Agent 启动失败**\n   - 内容：`Agent failed to start!`\n   - 出现次数：2\n   \n4. **Byteman触发器规则应用**\n   - 内容：`org.jboss.byteman.agent.Transformer : possible trigger for rule AdService-getRandomAds-latency-1749341416 in class hipstershop.AdService`\n   - 出现次数：1\n   \n5. **AdService触发点注入**\n   - 内容：`RuleTriggerMethodAdapter.injectTriggerPoint : inserting trigger into hipstershop.AdService.getRandomAds() java.util.List for rule AdService-getRandomAds-latency-1749341416`\n   - 出现次数：1\n   \n6. **触发器插入成功**\n   - 内容：`org.jboss.byteman.agent.Transformer : inserted trigger for AdService-getRandomAds-latency-1749341416 in class hipstershop.AdService`\n   - 出现次数：1\n\n### 分析和关键词提取\n根据日志内容，确定以下关键问题模块及关键词：\n- **确定日志关键点**:\n  - 错误类型及异常：`InvocationTargetException`, `Agent failed to start`, `attempting to load Byteman agent more than once`\n  - 触发规则：`AdService-getRandomAds-latency`\n  - 组件：`Byteman agent`, `hipstershop.AdService`\n  \n- **潜在的根因假设**:\n  - Byteman agent 的重复加载导致触发器插入失败。\n  - 由于 adservice 的代理模块 Byteman 配置或使用错误，服务的某些功能无法正常运行。\n\n### 输出 JSON 格式\n以下结果为提取的异常关键词与分析内容：\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\n    \"InvocationTargetException\",\n    \"Agent failed to start\",\n    \"attempting to load Byteman agent more than once\",\n    \"AdService-getRandomAds-latency\",\n    \"hipstershop.AdService\",\n    \"Byteman agent\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Byteman agent's duplicate loading attempt caused agent startup failure and rule trigger insertion issues.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Log contains repeat occurrence of 'Agent failed to start!' and 'attempting to load Byteman agent more than once'.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
